---
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../shared/Paragraph.astro";
import Title from "../shared/Title.astro";
---

<section id="features">
    <Container className="flex flex-col midmd:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="flex-1 flex midmd:w-7/12 lg:w-1/2 flex-col">
            <Title>
                Transform Your Online Presence into a Magnet for Serious Buyers
            </Title>
            <Paragraph className="mt-8">
                Buyers are tired of seeing the same posts and promotions
                everywhere. They don’t just want products, they crave solutions
                tailored to their needs. Let’s create a space that attracts them
                like bees to a flourishing garden. Here’s how:
            </Paragraph>
            <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-heading-3 font-medium">
                <li>
                    <span
                        class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center"
                        >&checkmark;</span
                    >
                    <strong> Stand Out in the Market:</strong> Transform your online
                    presence into a vibrant, solution-driven hub that buyers can't
                    resist.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span
                        class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center"
                        >&checkmark;</span
                    >
                    <strong> Provide Unique Solutions: </strong> Bundle your machinery,
                    maintenance plans, and value-added services into compelling offers
                    no competitor can match.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span
                        class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center"
                        >&checkmark;</span
                    >
                    <strong> Capture Every Opportunity:</strong> Build a seamless
                    system to nurture leads, deliver value, and guide them toward
                    becoming loyal customers.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span
                        class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 text-primary inline-flex justify-center items-center"
                        >&checkmark;</span
                    >
                    <strong> Make Data Work for You: </strong>
                    Leverage insights to refine your strategy, outshine competitors,
                    and foster lasting growth.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div
            class="max-w-md mx-auto midmd:max-w-none lg:mx-0 lg:pr-10 xl:pr-2 flex-1 flex w-11/12 midmd:w-5/12 lg:w-1/2 midmd:h-auto"
        >
            <div class="w-full h-80 sm:h-96 midmd:h-full relative">
                <div
                    class="absolute rotate-45 -left-5 md:-left-10 lg:-left-20 xl:-left-24 p-1 top-1/2 w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFC400] via-[#E5B300] to-[#BF9600] blur-3xl opacity-50"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute p-1 -top-4 md:-top-10 right-0 w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFC400] via-[#E5B300] to-[#BF9600] rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-60"
                >
                </div>

                <span
                    class="absolute w-full aspect-[16/5] -skew-x-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#FFC400] via-[#E5B300] to-[#BF9600] opacity-40 blur-2xl left-0 bottom-0"
                ></span>
                <img
                    src={"/images/excavator.png"}
                    alt="banner image"
                    width="1240"
                    height="1385"
                    class="w-auto left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 absolute bottom-0 max-h-full"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</section>
